---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Waypoint Talks"
  description="Learn about William Bierbower and the philosophy behind Waypoint Talks clarity coaching."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <!-- Image Placeholder -->
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-gold/20 to-brand-gold/5 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center p-8">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-brand-gold rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-white font-display font-bold text-5xl">W</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Photo coming soon</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Text Content -->
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display text-brand-navy mb-6">
              Hi, I'm William
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
              I founded Waypoint Talks because I believe <strong class="text-brand-navy">clarity takes space</strong> — and most of us don't give ourselves enough of it.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              We rush from decision to decision, second-guessing ourselves, overthinking every option. Sound familiar?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display text-brand-navy mb-8 text-center">
          Why Waypoint Talks Exists
        </h2>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-brand-gray space-y-6">
          <p>
            I've been where you might be right now — at a crossroads, overwhelmed by options, feeling disconnected from what actually matters. For years, I thought the answer was more information, more advice, more thinking.
          </p>

          <p>
            It wasn't. The answer was space. Space to slow down. Space to hear my own thoughts. Space to reconnect with my priorities without the noise of everyone else's opinions.
          </p>

          <p>
            That's what I offer through Waypoint Talks: a space to think out loud, untangle what's going on, and find your next step forward. Not therapy. Not consulting. Just clarity-focused conversations that leave you grounded and ready to move.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Approach Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display text-brand-navy mb-12 text-center">
          How I Work
        </h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-display font-bold text-xl">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-brand-navy mb-3">Start Where You Are</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray">
              There's no prep required. You don't need to have your thoughts organized or know exactly what you want to talk about. We start wherever you are.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-display font-bold text-xl">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-brand-navy mb-3">Create Space to Think</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray">
              I ask questions that help you hear yourself think. No judgment, no agenda — just genuine curiosity about what's going on for you.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-display font-bold text-xl">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-brand-navy mb-3">Find the Signal</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray">
              Together, we identify what actually matters underneath all the noise. Often it's not what you expected — and that's the breakthrough.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-display font-bold text-xl">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-brand-navy mb-3">Leave with Direction</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray">
              Every session ends with one clear insight and one concrete next step. You leave knowing exactly what to do — and feeling ready to do it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="section bg-brand-navy text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display mb-8">What I Believe</h2>

        <div class="grid gap-6 text-left">
          <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
            <p class="text-lg">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-semibold">Clarity isn't about having all the answers.</span>
              <span class="text-gray-300"> It's about knowing your next step.</span>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
            <p class="text-lg">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-semibold">You already have wisdom.</span>
              <span class="text-gray-300"> Sometimes you just need space to access it.</span>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
            <p class="text-lg">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-semibold">Action beats perfect planning.</span>
              <span class="text-gray-300"> One clear step forward is worth more than a hundred hypothetical paths.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display text-brand-navy mb-4">
          Ready to Find Your Clarity?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-8">
          Let's have a conversation. No pressure, no commitment — just a chance to explore what's possible.
        </p>
        <Button href="https://calendly.com/waypointtalks" external size="lg">
          Book a Free Intro Call
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
